Sentencas: Here it is demonstrated that the hierarchical BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-delta perovskite (BCFZY) cathode with 40-100 nm BCFZY nanoparticles uniformly decorated on porous BCFZY framework can be directly obtained through a reaction tuned formation process.
Titulo: Reaction tuned formation of hierarchical BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode

Sentencas: Triggered by the reaction with H2O, BCFZY surface layers exfoliate to nanocomposite particles on surfaces.
Titulo: Reaction tuned formation of hierarchical BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode

Sentencas: Uniformly dispersed nanocomposite particles on surfaces are achieved from the reaction of BCFZY with H2O and CO2 from the air.
Titulo: Reaction tuned formation of hierarchical BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode

Sentencas: These nanocomposite particles can be converted to polystructured BCFZY nanoparticles at temperatures above 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Reaction tuned formation of hierarchical BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode

Sentencas: The reactions to nanocomposite particles and then to BCFZY nanoparticles successively occur during sintering BCFZY cathode into the cell.
Titulo: Reaction tuned formation of hierarchical BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode

Sentencas: The single cell with the hierarchical BCFZY cathode outputs 1.61 W cm(-2) (2.30 A cm(-2)) at 0.70 V and 700 degrees C and exhibits an extremely low polarization resistance from oxygen reduction reaction.
Titulo: Reaction tuned formation of hierarchical BaCo0.4Fe0.4Zr0.1Y0.1O3-δ cathode
